Enables you to enter additional cess per item.
Enables you to keep your data safe, as Vyapar will take automatic backups to your google drive.
Enables auto sync feature, which allows you to synchronize data over multiple devices
Enables you to add barcode for every item and then use the barcode to scan items during sale and purchase transactions to make fast entries.
Enables you to create your company in Composite scheme for GST.
Enables you to select cash sale by default while creating new sale transaction.
Enables you to add discount in different transactions like Sale, Purchase etc. This field show up in the Item Details section and discount is applied on the subtotal of items added.
Enables you to change the party billing name on individual transactions.
Enables you to add E-way bill number in your transaction.
Enables you to create Estimate/Quotation transactions.

Enables you to add items that you sell and add them to your invoices and purchase bills etc.
Enables you to define unit of measure for your items. You will be able to define base unit, secondary unit and the conversion formula which will help you Sale and purhcase items in different units.
Enables you to add discount to every line ite in your sale and purchase transactions.
Enables you to add tax to every line item in your sale and purchase transactions.

Enables you to enable local language like hindi, gujrati, spanish, turkey etc. for your transaction pdfs. If you enter your party names, item names, description etc. in local language, then they get printed in the same format.

Enables you to track party wise item rate. Once enables, Vyapar will remember which item you are setting to which party at what price, and the it will show you that same price in the next transaction like sale and purchase.
Enables you to get automatic payment reminders that will help you follow up with your parties and get paid faster.

What is Vyapar Accounting App ?" Vyapar is an Accounting App that lets a business owner keep complete control of his business accounting, customer/supplier ledger, stock/inventory, Invoice creation and much more, anytime anywhere in a secure and private way. It helps you to be in full control of your business in a very simple and user friendly way.
VYAPAR IS MOST SAFE AND SIMPLE TO USE BUSINESS ACCOUNTING/BOOKKEEPING, CUSTOMER/SUPPLIER LEDGER, STOCK/INVENTORY MANAGEMENT APPLICATION AIMED AT SOLVING ALL THE ACCOUNTING/BOOKKEEPING NEEDS OF A BUSINESS OWNER.
"How will Vyapar Help your business ?" Vyapar is the most simple and easy to use Business Accounting App which you can learn to use in minutes and take complete control of all your business accounting activities like manage account books, party ledgers, inventory/stock etc.
• No worry about your data privacy as all data is stored only on your device and you take the control of where to keep the backup. Either to your personal accounts like gmail, google drive, drop box etc
• No need to memorize the balances as Vyapar reminds you for payments.
• Get paid faster by regular reminder to your parties for payment
• Generate digital invoices/bills in very less time and no need to maintain papers now. Send the invoices using any digital mechanism like email, whatsapp, sms etc.
• Know exact status of your inventory/stock so you always have the stock when a customer asks you.
• Keep clear view of your profit and loss, expenses, sales, purchases so that you can adjust your cashflow and bank account liquidity accordingly.
Lot more features like complete privacy and control of data, generating different reports to get clear view of overall business status, send digital bills to your parties to reduce the cost of paper, save time on matching party ledgers at the time of account settlements etc.
**It maintains "ALL THE BUSINESS ACCOUNTING DATA LOCALLY ON THE PHONE" and give owners complete control to take backup on phone or email.
*** Is available for a , which gives you complete access to explore the entire Accounting App and all it's features at your convenience to make an informed decision.
VYAPAR IS THE SIMPLEST TO USE BUSINESS ACCOUNTING APPLICATION IN THE WORLD!!
